rows.label: tlk42100151_05_msg0001
rows.name:
In the end, I stayed in Superbia.
It's surprisingly comfortable to live here.

rows.label: tlk42100151_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I've grown to like it, so I thought it
might not be so bad to end my days in Superbia.

rows.label: tlk42100151_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Thank you for listening to me.
You're the first human I've ever had a conversation with.
